{{ill|Nichu Shrine|ja|日雲神社|qq=draft}} is a {{ill|Moto-Ise Shrines|lt=Motoise shrine|ja|元伊勢|1=Moto-Ise Shrines|qq=draft}}.

Moto-Ise Shrines are {{ill|Shinto shrines|ja|神社|qq=draft}} that used to host Amaterasu before she was moved to {{ill|Ise Jingu|ja|伊勢神宮|qq=draft}}. The first one was {{ill|Hibara Shrine|ja|檜原神社|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Ōmiwa Shrine|ja|大神神社|qq=draft}}).

*
==Overview==
{{神社
|名称=日雲神社
|image=[[File:Hikumo-jinja.JPG|250px]]<br />日雲神社　拝殿
