** {{ill|Kasuga-taisha|lt=Kasuga-taisha|lt=Kasuga Shrine|ja|春日神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kasuga Shrine|qq=}}
** {{ill|Amemiya Shrine|ja|雨宮神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Amemiya Shrine|qq=}}
** {{ill|Itsukushima Shrine|ja|厳島神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Itsukushima Shrine|qq=}}
* Off-site Shrines
** {{ill|Kashima Jingu|lt=Kashima Jingu|lt=Kashima Shrine|ja|鹿島神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kashima Shrine|qq=}}

== Access ==
* A 5‑minute walk from {{ill|Shigaraki Kogen Railway|ja|信楽高原鐵道|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shigaraki Kogen Railway|qq=}}’s {{ill|Unoi Station|ja|雲井駅|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Unoi Station|qq=}}

